28 August 2015
Additions for the Gnome and Xfce DEs are now optional, and an option to
add tint2 has been added to Openbox. Password-entry has now been moved
to the end of the script for better security.

Previous ...

Extended functionality to 'scope' option - now adds luxuries such as web
browser, office suite, etc

New 'scope' option added for either full or basic installation.
'Reflector' added for better mirror-list.

Enlightenment Window Manager added.
Review option added. This is offered after all data-entry, and allows
user to check settings before installation begins.
